@startuml ProveoUsage
!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/refs/heads/main/proveo.iuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

left to right direction

title Proveo Command Entrypoints

actor "Consumer" as Consumer
actor "Maintainer" as Maintainer

package "Consumer / maintainer entrypoint\ncmd/proveo (static binary)" as Entrypoint {
 component "proveo" as Proveo <<app>>
 component "version · list · run · projects · setup" as Commands <<commands>>
 component "run flags\n--egress-mode · --local-model\n--scope · --shell · --print\n--image · --data-dir · --input · --output" as RunFlags <<commands>>
}

package "Installer" as Install {
 component "dist/install.sh\npin release + sha256 verify" as InstallSh <<script>>
 component "goreleaser artifacts\nlinux/darwin × amd64/arm64" as Artifacts <<image>>
}

package "Definition shims\ndefs/<target>/" as Shims {
 component "run.sh → proveo run <target>" as RunShim <<script>>
 component "build.sh · test.sh" as BuildTest <<script>>
}

package "Maintainer\nmise + lib/" as Maint {
 component "mise build|test|deploy" as Mise <<internal>>
 component "lib/build.sh · deploy.sh" as MaintLib <<script>>
}

package "Registration" as Reg {
 component "defs/*/harness.manifest\n(embedded in binary)" as Manifests <<config>>
}

package "Orchestration packages\ninternal/" as Orch {
 component "workspace mounts\napp | input-output" as Mounts <<logic>>
 component "egress BuildPlan\nbroker|proxy|firewall" as Egress <<logic>>
 component "dind (if dind: true)" as Dind <<logic>>
 component "runner hardened argv" as Runner <<logic>>
}

package "Runtime" as Runtime {
 component "Docker CLI" as Docker <<runtime>>
 component "proveo/* images" as Images <<image>>
 component "sidecars\nsquid · proveo-egress · ollama · dind" as Sidecars <<runtime>>
 component "workspace + state dir" as Storage <<storage>>
}

Consumer --> Install : first-time install
Install --> Artifacts
Install --> Proveo : places binary on PATH

Consumer --> Proveo : day-to-day
Maintainer --> Proveo : run / --print / list
Maintainer --> Mise : image lifecycle
Maintainer --> Shims : optional direct scripts

Proveo --> Commands
Commands --> RunFlags
Proveo --> Manifests : enumerate targets
Proveo --> Orch : compose plan
Orch --> Docker
Orch --> Images
Orch --> Sidecars
Orch --> Storage

RunShim ..> Proveo : exec
Mise ..> BuildTest
Mise ..> MaintLib
Mise ..> Proveo : run/list when needed
BuildTest --> Images

note right of Proveo
**Product CLI is Go only.**
No installed bash lib/*.sh runners.
""PROVEO_DEFS_DIR"" overrides embeds for dev.
end note

note right of RunFlags
""proveo run <target>"" applies to every
harness with a manifest (cecli, claudecode*,
opencode, cursor). Egress and DinD follow
manifest ""egress:"" / ""dind:"" flags.
end note

note bottom of Egress
Default ""--egress-mode firewall"": MITM
credential broker + Squid. ""--local-model""
adds Ollama (not for cursor). Session report
under the host state dir.
end note

@enduml
